{"tid":2491178,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭松泰：政府推廣國家安全教育時，不夠高明及聰明，無法帶出國安的真正含意。","createTime":"2021-04-16T06:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T07:43:46.000Z","uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"dc36730a95fbc4718377053419066481bf5f26e2","tid":2491178,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T06:22:51.000Z","msg":"黃竹坑警察學院在「國家安全教育日」開放予公眾參觀，有傳媒拍攝到有小學生模仿港鐵車廂內發生反恐事件，手持仿製槍指向同學。警務處長鄧炳強在立法會特別財委會表示，留意到今日有傳媒在頭版刊登相關照片，將天真爛漫的小朋友與暴力事件扯上關係，是非常不道德，質疑傳媒傷害小朋友的心，一旦有人親近警隊「就要搞佢」。教育局長楊潤雄則表示，不同人對同一張照片都有不同的聯想，大家不應該單憑一張照片就否定「全民國家安全教育日」的整體措施，或警方開放警察學院的安排，政府日後會汲取經驗，將來的推廣工作會做得更好。<br />\n<strong>熱血公民鄭松泰形容，相關照片對部分家長及市民是「震撼教育」，反映政府推廣國家安全教育時，不夠高明及聰明，令人勾起港鐵太子站8.31事件，無法帶出國安的真正含意。</strong><br />\n<br />\n[url]https://www-88<del><a href=\"http://1903-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2387466?amp_js_v=a6&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;usqp=mq331AQHKAFQArABIA%3D%3D#aoh=16185540454716&amp;csi=1&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshar\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F1903-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fv%2Fs%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Famp%2Flocal%2F2387466%3Famp_js_v%3Da6%26amp_gsa%3D1%26usqp%3Dmq331AQHKAFQArABIA%253D%253D%23aoh%3D16185540454716%26csi%3D1%26referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%26amp_tf%3D%25E4%25BE%2586%25E6%25BA%2590%25EF%25BC%259A%25251%2524s%26ampshar&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLaQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=7d74c2db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">1903-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/www.881903.com/news/amp/local/2387466?amp_js_v=a6&amp;amp_gsa=1&amp;usqp=mq331AQHKAFQArABIA%3D%3D#aoh=16185540454716&amp;csi=1&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E6%BA%90%EF%BC%9A%251%24s&amp;ampshar</a></del>e=https%3A%2F%<a href=\"http://2Fwww.881903.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F2Fwww.881903.com&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLaQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=88c338c7\" data-auto-link target=\"